            <title>[LU-18501] sanity test_56oe: Error:&apos;/usr/bin/lfs find /mnt/lustre/d56oe.sanity -ctime -19s -ctime +9s&apos; wrong: found 0, expected 5&apos;</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18501</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When the tests are running slow, it seems that the current time range is insufficient to find the desired files before they become too old. Calculating the time range based on file creation time should be enough to avoid this, but incase it&apos;s still too slow a check has been added to skip the test in that rare case.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
